---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Casey Irvine — Software Engineer, builder, and content creator.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">About</h1>

    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>
        Hey, I'm Casey. I started in music, but somewhere along the way I fell in love
        with math, building things with computers, and the feeling you get when something
        finally works.
      </p>
      <p>
        I started as an intern at Microsoft in the summer of 2010 and have pretty much
        been there ever since. I wouldn't call myself a great software engineer, but I'm
        a persistent one. I like making stuff, playing with new tech, and sharing what I learn.
      </p>
      <p>
        My interests wander: AI/ML, IoT, developer tools, and reinforcement learning.
        I've mentored junior engineers and led student RL projects, which is honestly
        some of the most rewarding work I've done.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is where I put the things I'm building and learning — through
        <a href="/articles">blog posts</a> and <a href="/videos">short-form videos</a>.
        No expertise required. Just curiosity.
      </p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Find me elsewhere</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/cirvine-MSFT">GitHub</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://youtube.com/@CaseyIrvine">YouTube</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
